Command line cross platform reddit reader 
Windows & Mac OS

Usage:

r: Copyright 2012 Roland Rabien
  usage: r [-lpiocadv] [-n max] subreddit
  -l Open links (default)
  -p Open permalinks
  -i Open Imgur links only
  -o Open subreddit
  -c Clear history
  -a Open all (including previously opened)
  -n Maximum number of links to open (default 30)
  -h Display help
  -v Display version

Examples:

r -n 100 pics  # open lastest 100 links in pics
r -p jokes     # open 30 lastest comments pages in jokes
r -o vertical  # go to the veritcal subreddit

Download:
Mac - http://downloads.rabien.com/r.tar.gz
Windows - http://downloads.rabien.com/r.zip
